results_by_precinct, results_by_council_district, seattle_cd_shapes = \
    et.import_and_aggregate(precinct_shapes_file=PRECINCT_DATA,
                            district_shapes_file=SEATTLE_COUNCIL_DISTRICT_SHAPES,
                            precinct_results_file=PRECINCT_RESULTS,
                            districts_by_precinct_file=DISTRICT_ASSIGNMENTS,
                           dra_data=True,
                           missing_precinct_list=MISSING_PRECINCTS)
